"samps = \"/path/to/my/samples/\"\n"
"sample samps, \"120\""
msgstr ""
"samps = \"/path/to/my/samples/\"\n"
"sample samps, \"120\""

#: 03.7-Sample-Packs.md:112
msgid ""
"This will play us the first match. If we want the second match we just need to"
" use the index:"
