#: 11.2-MIDI-Out.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "midi_note_on :e3, channel: 3"
msgstr ""

#: 11.2-MIDI-Out.md:76
msgid ""
"Of course we can also specify both at the same time to send to a specific devi"
"ce on a specific channel:"
